text: The JAC Refine S4 is a compact Crossover SUV made by JAC Motors from 2018 to 2022. == History and Features == The JAC Refine S4 was launched in October 2018 its slightly positioned above the JAC Refine S3 and below the JAC Refine S5. the Refine S4 has a 1.5 liter turbo and 1.6 liter petrol engines with a 6-speed manual or CVT transmissions. It has a electric version called JAC iEVS4 this version has three versions:one with a 55 kWh battery with a range of 355 km (221 mi) other with a 61 kWh battery with a range of 402 km (249 mi) and a version with a 66 kWh battery with a range of 470 km (292 mi). == Markets == The JAC Refine S4 was sold mainly in the Chinese market but in some places outside China it was sold as the JAC T60 and in Mexico it was made through kits CKD in Ciudad Sahag√∫n and was sold as the JAC Sei 4. == Discontinuation == The production of The Refine S4 ended in 2022 and was eventually discontinued without a sucessor. == References == Category:Chinese automobiles Category:2010s automobiles Category:2020s automobiles Category:Sport utility vehicles
